ygData.msgSnippet: Go to www.onelist.com, login and then it will take you to the member center where the lists you are subscribed to will show up.. click the word unsubscribe at
ygData.messageBody:
Go to www.onelist.com, login and then it will take you to the member center
where the lists you are subscribed to will show up.. click the word
unsubscribe at the end of the list you want to remove yourself from.
Should work, if it doesn't I have NO clue. :)
